Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.70,0:02:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时还以为她已经不行了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师能重新振作起来真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.20,0:02:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为出现了后继者又提起劲头了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.30,0:02:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.60,0:02:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师 好久没见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.70,0:02:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 哎呀 这位是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 红老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.50,0:02:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是在电视上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是我们公司的艺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫来岛薰子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是红 请多关照啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.70,0:02:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是老师的忠实影迷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能再观赏到老师的戏剧女流侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.70,0:02:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在好期待呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.70,0:02:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加油 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.10,0:02:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么老师 待会儿见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.30,0:02:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}太棒了 一直那么成熟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个可爱的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 彩花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被别人说“现在好期待”呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能把戏演砸了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.70,0:03:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 你是大街上的垂柳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么晃晃悠悠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没有刮风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.60,0:03:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是棵柳树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静静伫立在河边的柳树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你要我说几次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不像是为了培养未来的招牌女演员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒像是为了虐待她而收养的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有那回事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 人家会这个说也没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩花真是可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.30,0:04:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}龟裂的面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.80,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.50,0:04:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你呼唤我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱 少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.90,0:04:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.80,0:04:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.50,0:04:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.20,0:05:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.30,0:05:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再考虑下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收我为养女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我的演技应该是被认可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这羞辱又算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下地狱去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦 彩花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这年纪了还在玩人偶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.00,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 样子还真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要诅咒杀了谁吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真罗嗦 不用你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 彩花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能借我点钱吗 十万左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.90,0:06:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要那么多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我那么好骗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被户好人家收养了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点钱不算什么 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个累赘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.30,0:06:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 靠地狱通信或许还不如找这两个白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不可以借给你们 有个条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.80,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是彩花 通情达理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么我都会听的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施舍点钱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们肚子饿扁了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去 不然我要大叫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.60,0:07:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看啊 在这之前先打烂你的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 胆子可不小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我老实点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.20,0:07:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把钱给我拿出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.20,0:07:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你 你干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 再不出去我要报警了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐 给我记着 我会找你算帐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.70,0:08:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的那些男青年还真没骨气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没有受伤吧 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一还是报警吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.80,0:08:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那两个人难道是你以前的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上几天前他们就纠缠着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.10,0:08:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还威胁要把以前的一些事向媒体暴光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 既然出了这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我就到警署去报警抓他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够相信你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.90,0:08:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 这么晚了你上哪干什么去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在排练场做柳树的练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够演好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.10,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我会努力的  决不会给著名女演员红翠的后继者这个名分抹黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.00,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很晚了 去睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事得通知小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.70,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐会怎么做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.70,0:09:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次公演的女流侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.00,0:09:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是推理作家身边出现了一名自称是她崇拜者的年轻女子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开一场死亡游戏的对手戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是团长的出道作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.50,0:09:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前团长演过的年轻女孩角色还没决定好由谁扮演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过肯定会选彩花的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.80,0:09:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩花演戏演得很好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.10,0:09:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 是看中了彩花的演技才收她为养女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.30,0:09:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团长也将这次公演作为最后演出然后引退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像以后的都打算交给彩花吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.00,0:10:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团长由彩花接替 大家都赞成吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的问题呢 当然赞成啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩花既认真 又不摆架子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团长的通知 所有人到练习室集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.80,0:10:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都到齐了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.40,0:10:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在公布下次公演中与我演对手戏的人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天终于来到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐到今天也算值得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来岛熏子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.90,0:10:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾演过电视剧 大家想必也认识吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的对手将由她来扮演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来岛 请多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是彩花啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到突然找了外面的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.10,0:11:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事 这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常荣幸 红老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到能够出演女流侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.90,0:11:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是做梦一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待你的表现 加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.00,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个臭女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.80,0:11:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我能力不够吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你还不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪里不足 请跟我说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.60,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.00,0:11:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情和声音就是演戏的话你就大错特错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.80,0:11:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一根手指的动作没有用心体会 那就不是演戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装傻了 就是昨晚的那事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无可救药的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这么拙劣的戏就别演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.60,0:11:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在因为公演的事我已经很忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会分心的 所以请出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不甘心的话 就把演技磨练得更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不会 我的演技应该是完美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那两个家伙走漏风声了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.40,0:12:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 那烂透了的演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.70,0:12:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那种本事也想取代我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸简直比犀牛皮还厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点自己退出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 只要让她退出就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.00,0:12:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我们可没走漏风声啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就当是这么回事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 就是为这事打电话给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 如果加倍付钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能再拜托你件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.30,0:13:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来岛 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁 到底是谁做出这么过分的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 彩花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.50,0:13:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是为了我的话 请不要做这种事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.10,0:13:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没有介意 是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的事谢谢你啊 彩花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.10,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 接下这角色很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也一直觉得很对不起彩花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不用放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样一开始拒绝不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.30,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在策划什么阴谋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 开心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那个 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很晚了 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.70,0:14:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早嘛 好不容易我们成了朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦 可爱的小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.30,0:14:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这女孩么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.00,0:14:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超靓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 之后就拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩…彩花 等下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 你来这边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让…让我回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.10,0:14:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不让你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 积点德吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天还有重要的练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 喝了就让你走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让声音变得动听无比的药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.40,0:14:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.30,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 一口气喝掉就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.80,0:15:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熏子好像发不出声音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊 是不是压力太大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是那么地努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.00,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 要恨的话就恨这个女人吧 熏子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让团员在排练场集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有重要通知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将主角换作我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我要通知什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.30,0:15:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次公演终止 剧团也一并解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.10,0:16:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且断绝与你的养母女关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你干的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫你不要再演这么拙劣的戏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再糊涂了 你可骗不了我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.90,0:16:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是误会 之前那晚的事情真的不关我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.40,0:16:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妈妈收养的时候 我就像是重生了一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够跟妈妈您相遇真的是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.10,0:16:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了妈妈我才能了解到演戏的乐趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并找到了活下去的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是多么感谢妈妈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不像样 快放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 我已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事也已经告诉顾问律师了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后就永别了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.60,0:16:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你这臭老太婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.30,0:17:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤心啊 说什么臭老太婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要说那么让人伤心的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今所做的一切都是为了你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然教导或许过于严格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.80,0:17:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的所作所为无法让人原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.30,0:17:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果你能够承认自己所犯的错误并为此改过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.80,0:17:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时如果你还想继续演戏的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.90,0:17:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把你介绍给朋友的剧团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.90,0:17:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 还可以从头再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.70,0:17:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的才能肯定能成为一个出色的演员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.80,0:17:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是烦人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唠叨已经够多的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.80,0:17:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能继承你的名号谁会来陪你玩什么过家家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.60,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法得到你的财产和名声的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.00,0:17:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就根本没有意义 不明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.70,0:18:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情成了现在这样 真是很可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.00,0:18:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说可惜就完了吗 混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我也不管那么多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然走到了这步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.80,0:18:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在养母女关系解除前她死掉的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.70,0:18:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少财产可以归我所有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下地狱去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.00,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.80,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.80,0:18:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这是怎么了 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.60,0:18:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有人先解开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.10,0:18:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.20,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人昨晚登录了地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才解开了红线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.00,0:19:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经晚了一步 请放弃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我在先的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事 回答我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 慢着 等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.00,0:19:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备认罪了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.30,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不认罪的话就会坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.30,0:19:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.60,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我认罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是谁的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 剧演错了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.90,0:19:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台词不是口头上 而是要发自内心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我觉得熏子她真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.70,0:20:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你这戏真糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太低级趣味了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.20,0:20:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么 发生了什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.20,0:20:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.90,0:20:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 好痛 好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.50,0:20:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 戏已经演够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.10,0:20:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要听的不是你的台词 而是你真心话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.80,0:20:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请相信我 这就是真实的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.90,0:20:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对 不是这样的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.60,0:21:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么想听我就说给你们听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.00,0:21:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演戏根本就无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说不过是个台阶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.10,0:21:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 好不容易学到的演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在该骗人的时候就要骗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.90,0:21:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时是谁都尊敬的著名女演员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.00,0:21:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时又是高贵的夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.10,0:21:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而有的时候又是充满丑闻的魔性之女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.10,0:21:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时又是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.20,0:21:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 到底哪个是真实的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.10,0:21:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.60,0:21:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.90,0:21:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.90,0:22:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很逼真的演技啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.60,0:22:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你至今为止最出色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.40,0:22:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.70,0:22:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.90,0:22:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 借过一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 拿一下扳手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.90,0:22:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.90,0:23:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
