Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.60,0:24:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.40,0:24:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田沼千恵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.10,0:24:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.60,0:24:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他的错 祐子她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.10,0:24:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是爱他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.90,0:24:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的爱着他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.30,0:24:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.40,0:24:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将他流放到地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.80,0:24:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
